          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Eliminating CECL Accounting Standard Act</b></p> <p>This bill provides that no one shall be required to comply with a specified accounting standard applicable to credit losses (i.e., the current expected credit losses standard, also known as the CECL standard).</p>]]></text>
